            <title>[LU-19980] Improve lock_manager_operations tests</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19980</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Configure tests that use &quot;struct lock_manager_operations lm_ops&quot; will fail after:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Linux commit v6.2-rc3-9-g5970e15dbcfe&lt;br/&gt;
filelock: move file locking definitions to separate header file&lt;/p&gt;

